statements: SELECT * FROM real_time_data;
SELECT id, data_type, value, timestamp FROM real_time_data;
SELECT data_type FROM real_time_data WHERE id = 1;
SELECT value, timestamp FROM real_time_data ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT id, data_type, value FROM real_time_data WHERE value > 100;
SELECT id, timestamp, data_type, value FROM real_time_data WHERE data_type = 'temperature' ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT id, data_type, value FROM real_time_data WHERE value > 100 ORDER BY id;
SELECT * FROM real_time_data WHERE data_type = 'humidity' AND value < 50 ORDER BY timestamp;
SELECT id, timestamp, value FROM real_time_data WHERE value BETWEEN 50 AND 100 ORDER BY value DESC;
SELECT id, timestamp, data_type FROM real_time_data WHERE timestamp >= '2022-01-01' AND timestamp < '2023-01-01' ORDER BY data_type, timestamp DESC;
SELECT * FROM real_time_streaming_data WHERE event_id = 1;
SELECT event_name, event_timestamp FROM real_time_streaming_data WHERE event_timestamp > '2022-01-01';
SELECT event_id, event_name, event_timestamp FROM real_time_streaming_data WHERE event_name LIKE '%error%';
SELECT event_id, event_timestamp, event_data FROM real_time_streaming_data WHERE event_timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-01-31';
SELECT result_id, event_id, result_description, analysis_timestamp FROM analysis_result WHERE analysis_timestamp < NOW();
SELECT * FROM real_time_streaming_data WHERE event_name = 'Click' ORDER BY event_timestamp DESC;
SELECT event_id, event_name, event_timestamp FROM real_time_streaming_data WHERE event_timestamp > '2021-01-01' AND event_data->>'user' = 'Alice';
SELECT event_id, event_name, event_timestamp FROM real_time_streaming_data WHERE event_data->'action' @> '["purchase"]' ORDER BY event_timestamp ASC LIMIT 10;

SELECT r.result_id, a.event_name, r.result_description, r.analysis_timestamp FROM analysis_result r JOIN real_time_streaming_data a ON r.event_id = a.event_id WHERE r.result_description LIKE '%error%' ORDER BY r.analysis_timestamp;
SELECT event_id, event_name, COUNT(*) AS event_count FROM real_time_streaming_data GROUP BY event_id, event_name HAVING COUNT(*) > 5 ORDER BY event_count DESC, event_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM RealTimeStreams;
SELECT stream_id, stream_name FROM RealTimeStreams WHERE stream_name = 'example';
SELECT stream_name, stream_data FROM RealTimeStreams ORDER BY stream_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM StreamAnalytics WHERE analytic_type = 'prediction' ORDER BY analytic_id DESC;
SELECT stat_timestamp, stat_value FROM StreamStatistics WHERE stat_value > 100 ORDER BY stat_timestamp DESC;
SELECT * FROM RealTimeStreams;
SELECT stream_name, stream_data FROM RealTimeStreams WHERE stream_id='123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT * FROM StreamAnalytics ORDER BY analytic_type DESC;
SELECT stream_id, COUNT(*) FROM StreamStatistics GROUP BY stream_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 10;
SELECT stream_name, stat_timestamp FROM RealTimeStreams JOIN StreamStatistics ON RealTimeStreams.stream_id = StreamStatistics.stream_id WHERE StreamStatistics.stat_timestamp > '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM RealTimeData;
SELECT id, timestamp FROM RealTimeData ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT stream_name, description FROM DataStreams WHERE stream_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT * FROM StreamAnalytics WHERE analytics_type = 'average';
SELECT consumer_name FROM DataConsumers WHERE subscription_status = TRUE;
SELECT * FROM RealTimeData WHERE id = 1;
SELECT stream_name, description FROM DataStreams WHERE stream_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT stream_id, analytics_type, result_data FROM StreamAnalytics WHERE analytics_id > 5 ORDER BY analytics_id DESC;
SELECT * FROM DataConsumers WHERE consumer_name = 'John' AND subscription_status = TRUE;
SELECT id, timestamp, data_payload->'field' AS field_value FROM RealTimeData ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT * FROM RealTimeAnalytics ORDER BY event_timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT event_id, event_type FROM RealTimeAnalytics WHERE event_type = 'click';
SELECT * FROM StreamSources WHERE source_type = 'API';
SELECT source_name, source_location FROM StreamSources ORDER BY source_name ASC;
SELECT * FROM DataProcessing WHERE process_status = 'completed';
SELECT * FROM RealTimeAnalytics ORDER BY event_timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT event_id, event_timestamp, event_type FROM RealTimeAnalytics WHERE event_type = 'Click' ORDER BY event_timestamp ASC;
SELECT source_name, source_type, source_location FROM StreamSources WHERE source_location LIKE '%USA%';
SELECT process_id, process_name FROM DataProcessing WHERE process_status = 'completed';
SELECT result_id, result_timestamp, result_data FROM StreamResults ORDER BY result_timestamp DESC;
